Usage:

To compile
gfortran -c -o pwhg_cpHTO.o pwhg_cpHTO_reweight.f

To call from C++
program.cc:

  extern"C" {
    void pwhg_cphto_reweight_(double *mh, double *gh, double *mt, int *BWflag, double *m, double *w);
  }

  double w;
  pwhg_cphto_reweight_(&mh, &gh, &mt, &BWflag, &m, &w); 

then
g++ -o program program.cc pwhg_cpHTO.o -lgfortran
